k_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3pk","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":15205,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/21\/gold-silver-vessels-furniture\/","url_meta":{"origin":13102,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Vanity: Using expensive vessels and silk furniture","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited us from eating and drinking out of golden or silver vessels. He prohibited us from wearing silk or brocade, or sitting upon anything made from them. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5499,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2067 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15292,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/extravagance-gold-silver-silk\/","url_meta":{"origin":13102,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Luxury: Prohibition of silk clothes, gold dishes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Do not drink from gold or silver vessels, and do not wear silk or brocade. Verily, these are for unbelievers in the world and for us in the Hereafter.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5633, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2067 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43175,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/16\/men-wearing-silk\/","url_meta":{"origin":13102,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Silk: Prohibition of men wearing silk","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 16, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not wear silk, for whoever wears silk in the world will not wear it in the Hereafter.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2069 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5026,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/12\/men-silk\/","url_meta":{"origin":13102,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Silk: What can men do with silk?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: Umar bought a silk cloak from the market and took it to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, take it and wear it on Eid and when the delegations visit you.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThis clothing is for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15415,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/prophet-seven-commands\/","url_meta":{"origin":13102,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ahkam: Seven prohibitions and commands","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara' ibn 'Azib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited us from seven things: using gold rings, silk, flax, brocade, red saddle clothes, taffeta, and silver vessels. And the Prophet commanded us to do seven things: to visit the sick, to follow the funeral procession, to bless\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34415,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/09\/27\/ummah-endangered-by-five\/","url_meta":{"origin":13102,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Vice: Ummah is endangered by five evil practices","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen my nation adopts five practices, their destruction is inevitable: when they curse each other openly, they wear silk, they take up musical instruments, they drink wine, and men are satisfied with men and women are satisfied\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13102","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}